{"tid":1751822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"理大手足我地冇唔記得你地","createTime":"2019-11-24T18:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T19:15:31.000Z","uid":278101,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c7a573a248ce5258ad783c7a0649685837e4c9f","tid":1751822,"uid":278101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:14:22.000Z","msg":"一路睇點票一路都會諗，<br />\n唔知理大手足有冇一齊睇緊？<br />\n你地睇緊既話係咩感受？<br />\n<br />\n一直有人諗住你地嫁。<br />\n加油撐住！<br />\n<br />\n運動以來既每一個決定都推動緊唔同既改變。<br />\n血債絕對唔能夠票償，<br />\n但我諗今屆區選既各樣破記錄，<br />\n都係哩幾個月我地做既大大小小努力推動而成。<br />\n<br />\n睇到何已完開心，<br />\n睇到老鼠芬落敗開心，<br />\n係因為見到多少少希望。<br />\n希望大家開心完一齊諗下一步要點做，<br />\n有更多既改變我地就有更大既機會贏！<br />\n贏，先對得住做左咁多犧牲既各位手足！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ab7c1e5a5ce0eedf1933b5aa868033e75c623c","tid":1751822,"uid":252877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:35:23.000Z","msg":"泛民記得要救手足呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94601b20e1fddc68b83232449c456456b652dccd","tid":1751822,"uid":87189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:38:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1174e4087abcdbcf23dd0b5833d0755d41de7c01","tid":1751822,"uid":341842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces